+
+<h3><a name="What's_still_to_do_">What's Still To Do?</a></h3>
+
+<p>See list of what we think needs to be done, and consider helping out if
+you're interested &amp; able!</p>
+<ol type="1">
+  <li>JAX-RPC 1.1 and/or JAX-WS compliance</li>
